# Cloud Agent PR Workflow

When a cloud agent is working on a pull request, it should **not** run the
final verification check (e.g. the build/lint/test verification pass that
normally happens before wrapping up).

- Make the requested changes as usual.
- Skip the final verification step — CI on the PR is responsible for that.
- Note in the summary that final verification was skipped (handled by CI).
